videos.description: Khris Middleton's shot is off the mark, but Giannis Antetokounmpo is right there for a putback jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis cleans up Middleton's miss with dunk) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis cleans up Middleton's miss with dunk

videos.description: Cameron Payne gets trapped so he dishes to Cam Johnson for a 3-pointer from the wing.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Johnson drops in 3-pointer with ease) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson drops in 3-pointer with ease

videos.description: After Devin Booker's shot gets blocked, Cam Johnson dishes to Deandre Ayton for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Suns fans erupt after Ayton's dunk) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Suns fans erupt after Ayton's dunk

videos.description: During a timeout, Giannis Antetokounmpo passionately tries to keep the Bucks focused in Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis tries to fire up his team) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis tries to fire up his team

videos.description: Deandre Ayton tries to throw down a dunk, but Jrue Holiday jumps high to block the attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Holiday denies Ayton at the rim) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Holiday denies Ayton at the rim

videos.description: Suns put their passing on display as they find Deandre Ayton underneath for an and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Suns display phenomenal ball movement leading to Ayton's and-1) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Suns display phenomenal ball movement leading to Ayton's and-1

videos.description: Phoenix's Mikal Bridges throws down a two-handed jam that has the Suns' bench on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bridges kicks off second half with huge dunk) 2021/7/8 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges kicks off second half with huge dunk

videos.description: Chris Paul is left wide open in the corner and drains the trey as the shot clock expires.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 beats shot clock buzzer with corner 3) 2021/7/8 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 beats shot clock buzzer with corner 3

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo becomes the first player with 20 points or more in a single NBA Finals quarter in the last 25 seasons.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Giannis scores historic amount of points in third quarter) 2021/7/8 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Giannis scores historic amount of points in third quarter

videos.description: Devin Booker hits back-to-back 3-pointers as the Suns extend their lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Booker hits back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Torrey Craig hurts his right knee taking a charge and would exit to the locker room.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Torrey Craig exits with right knee injury) 2021/07/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Torrey Craig exits with right knee injury

videos.description: Devin Booker breaks down why he sat the last few minutes of the Suns' win and what the team's mentality is heading into Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Booker: Suns going into '0-0 mindset' heading into Game 3) 2021/7/8 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker: Suns going into '0-0 mindset' heading into Game 3

videos.description: The Suns' starters all reach double digits as Phoenix overcomes Giannis Antetokounmpo's 42 points to take a 2-0 series lead in the NBA Finals.

videos.headline: Suns' collective effort pushes them to 2-0 Finals lead
